                  "html": "<p>In this characteristically naturalistic view, Constable accurately depicts the terrain along the Stour River, applying intense attention to details of foliage, weather, and light. The cloud-filled sky creates drama and an evocative mood. Moving beyond idealized classicism, Constable pioneered a naturalism that romanticized common rural life and landscapes. His dedication to portraying transient effects directly observed in nature was groundbreaking.</p>",
